Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Success! Integrity! Evidence and its impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An endless drive to become the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:05.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The year gets off to an unwelcome start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A case turns up as Ran gets a heart-shocking love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Kitada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from Class C got dumped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonoko! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:02:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about cooking something good for Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. He hasn't been eating any dinner lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful young schoolgirl like you shouldn't be thinking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you could learn something from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll head home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bag, so wait for me by the shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.18,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:32.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd better open it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:48.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S.H.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it in my shoes locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:11.10,Title,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just rip it open already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Please forgive me for sending you this letter so suddenly."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Whenever I'm thinking about you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}, I can feel my heart beating. I can't even sleep at night."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I would like to meet you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll be waiting for you tomorrow after school, at the fountain in Beika Park."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Ran! It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you "Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}", he has to be a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know you already have Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with Shin'ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't even have a simple conversation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you got a love letter?\NI haven't had any in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's the first time you got one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, so nobody sends you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you this has nothing to do with Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a former {\i1}kendō{\i0} club member?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's holding a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind that, focus on the love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go, right? To Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go and turn him down in a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll say you already have a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}do{\i0} look worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no choice. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll turn him down for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to turn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look weird, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! She got her very first love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh, my beloved Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll hold you close and place a loving kiss on your sweet lips..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's lying, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you really {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're interested, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a bit interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a first-year student with the initials "S. H.".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A first-year student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to meet her tomorrow at the fountain in Beika Park after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran doesn't know how to handle it, so I'm going to go and turn him down instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:08.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. And I can't do anything. Who could've sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do? Can I really\Njust leave it to Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's mine if he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something's bothering you, you can talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father's the great detective Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her husband's the high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Detective Mouri, and the high-school detective Kudō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be a Teitan High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're second-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should talk about it with you, like that boy suggested...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can, right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you don't mind speaking to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll help you, {\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in! Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stayed in the hospital for six months and fought hard, but he couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it seems someone broke into my house while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went for a walk with Yūto for two hours at around 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I must've forgotten to lock that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I usually personally hand the rent to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I withdrew some money from the bank this morning and put it in this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems the money I had in here was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was put back. All the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how do you know it was taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the money was folded even though you got new notes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's a very faint fold though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I always leave my diary here too, but it looks like someone's been reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best proof is that someone burnt an incense stick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was still burning when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much of the stick was left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the incense stick was lit about 15 minutes before you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, incense sticks usually last about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat always knows strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone really broke into this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is who broke in and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He read the diary, so isn't he a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But except for that diary, it didn't look like anything had been looked through or taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though a thief wouldn't bring the money back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's hard to imagine a thief lighting up an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a little bit uncomfortable, so I asked a policeman to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since nothing was taken,\Nthere wasn't anything to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The incense stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the most intriguing part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the culprit one of her acquaintances, or one of her husband's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, how did you meet your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really a curious brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a classmate of mine in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we had no feelings for each other back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduating from university, we happened to meet each other in the city and started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not like Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, you said someone read your diary, but what was written in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like "working and taking care of a child everyday is tough,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"but I get some strength when I think about him." Childish stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be really hard being alone, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I already thought about committing suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a child, and thought about my late husband who struggled so hard with his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not just my husband. There are so many people who want to live but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'd be unforgivable for me to give up my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so sad, I'm shedding tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe the culprit felt the same way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's true, our culprit would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw on TV that a thief broke into a house and left without stealing anything after changing his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was the house of a teacher who'd been kind to him when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he broke in without knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, you wouldn't happen to be a school teacher, would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you weren't their teacher, you could be somebody they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More to the point, you could be somebody special to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write a diary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they read said special person's diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diary that shows so clearly that you're living honestly despite many misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why they didn't take anything and instead just lit an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he even sent you a love letter during high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking, Sonoko! We're being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, {\i1}senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The January of my third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it hadn't been for that letter,\NI wouldn't even know his name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never been in the same class at all, from first year to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently he'd always been admiring me, and I just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king of one-sided love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter said he wanted to meet me at the fountain in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hesitated, but I went to tell him my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad you have those feelings for me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"but I can't think of anything other than the entrance exams right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that, he just left without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shūhei Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, were you part of the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was the manager during my 2nd year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought. That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, he's the one who broke into your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, have you heard from him since you graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, about two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one of my husband's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never spoke about him to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came up in conversation as one of the many other classmates we had at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:11.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He did his best, but he couldn't enter the university he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:15.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And after graduating, he only found a job in a company he didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:19.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, he quit that company, and it seems he's doing part-time jobs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}, by any chance did you enter a top university just after high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'd call it a top university, but I {\i1}did{\i0} enter the university I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to hear my deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After meeting Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} at the Beika Park fountain, Shūhei Nagai didn't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But feeling inferior to her, who'd entered a top university just after high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't bring himself to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after graduation, as his professional life wasn't any good either,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he ended up without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As he was already familiar with Beika District, he chose it to commit his theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he was headed to a rich mansion, probably mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way there, he noticed the window in your house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He figured out the house was empty, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman in the photo was the one he'd fallen in love with in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also remembered the man with her as a high school classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from the picture on the altar, he realized that the classmate in question had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while he knew it was wrong, he also read the diary he'd found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He found out about how you were doing your best to live on with your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and thought about his classmate who died in his 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he started feeling ashamed of himself, as he was taking advantage of people despite still being healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I see Ran put so much effort into her karate practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sometimes think I should work hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Shūhei Nagai decided to redeem himself, and so he put the money back in the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,burnt a stick in honor of his late classmate, and left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, as he knew he would never come back to this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to see the school he graduated from one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that just happened to be when the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club was practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he remembered Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} and started reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be staring at the fountain in Beika Park now even!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was almost the same as what I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Nagai guy who I saw in front of the gymnasium seemed a little bit different than you deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked rather languished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I still don't know why he was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}shinai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, was there anything else written in the diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's actually something I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 days ago, I was involved in a small accident with a man riding a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he said everything was OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came back later saying he couldn't turn his head any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him that I'd pay for his medical fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he asked for a "relationship" instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite persistently, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seemed like a pretty bad guy, so I was afraid something might happen to my son if I'd rejected him too harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I didn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was he today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's on a business trip until tonight, and I don't think he was today's intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you just told us was written in your diary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this Nagai guy was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you that girl's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And keep your hands off her kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What are you blabbering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sayin'? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you couldn't turn your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You despicable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, it seems you can't turn your neck for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read your diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so glad you'd come to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. I'll go there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what I'll say, but I have to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him my sincerity for having written that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:36.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:46.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran said she wanted to tell him the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:49.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she mean about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd wait for you, but you ended up being the one waiting for me, {\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:03.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}, the captain of the karate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a first-year boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! And Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I was gonna hear Ran's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're able to grasp women's hearts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
